0 PRACTICE~
Syntax: PRACTICE
Syntax: PRACTICE <skill|spell|prayer|song|chant>

PRACTICE without an argument tells you your current ability level in all
the skills and spells available to you.  You can check this anywhere.

PRACTICE with an argument practice that skill or spell.  If you have the exp
