You lose experience by fleeing from combat, recalling out of combat,
being the target of certain spells and dying.

If you are in a group, the experience points you gain together is divided
among the group members using the shares system.  [help group] will give
you more details on how the shares system works.

Your character gains in power as it levels, increasing in statistics
and skills alike.  Your hitpoint gains depend on your strength and
constitution; your mana on intelligence and wisdom.

Note that level gains are based on your natural stats, not on equipment
enhanced stats.

See also [help practice] and [help gain].
~

