right after remort.  Anything that you gain while Kalian is NOT added 
to your total xp.  If you decide that you do not like the race, then you  
can reincarnate.  You go back to the race that you were before with no
loss of xp.  You do not change classes while Kalian, either.  When you
remort, then you must stay the same classes you were before the remort.

